      "date": "2013-01-25 15:19:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Looks good to me, approved\n\nWe should probably also remove the PLAIN to IBITS  lock type conversion on the MDS. This was added in Lustre 1.4 fir compatibility when IBITS locking was first developed, but is not needed anymore, and is now causing problems like this. That would also simplify the DNE update to allow both PLAIN and IBITS locks on the same connection.",
